videos.title: How to Delete All Files With the Same Extension Using Command Prompt
videos.description: In this video, I show you how to delete all of a certain file type in a folder using Command Prompt in Windows. This can be very useful when managing files for a project, where there are many of an unnecessary file type mixed in with your project.
videos.author: Learn with Ashik

videos.title: Knockpy : Best Subdomain Finder and Subdomain Enumeration Tool
videos.description: Knockpy is a python tool designed to enumerate subdomains on a target domain through a wordlist. It is designed to scan for DNS zone transfer and to try to bypass the wildcard DNS record automatically if it is enabled. Now knockpy supports queries to VirusTotal subdomains, you can setting the API_KEY within the config.json file.
